Package one.group.models.repositories

Class TablesRepo

java.lang.Object
one.group.models.repositories.TablesRepo
public class TablesRepo extends Object
Class to act as a repositoty for the information regarding the csv files used by the program. Uses static fields and methods. Includes methods to store each csv file as an ArrayList on boot, get methods only return copies.
